brand.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</article></article>', 'Basic On UI And UX Design Tricks by Steve Jobs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-10 09:42:56', '2018-02-10 09:42:56', '', 38, 'http://localhost/Xploiting/2018/02/10/38-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
